{'name': 'Ivan Ma', 'bio': 'Ivan Ma is the MySQL User Group Lead in Hong Kong. He has over 20+ years of experience in enterprise system infrastructure and software technologies. 

He Joined MySQL, is currently MySQL Master Principal Solution Engineer and is responsible for pre-sales solutions, technical exchange, and product promotions with community users and customers.

Prior to joining MySQL team, he joined Oracle in System Team from Sun Mircosystems acquisition. Prior to Sun Microsystems, he was Principal Solution Architect with Sybase APAC covering APAC regions.'}

